text: "Feel Alright" is a hip-hop song by Kardinal Offishall. It was the third single from his third album Fire and Glory. A music video, directed by RT!, was released for the single. ==Track listing== ===12" single=== A-side #"Feel Alright" (Clean) #"Feel Alright" (Main) #"Feel Alright" (Instrumental) B-side #"E.G.G."
